description:
The fabulous Erika Jayne (THE REAL HOUSEWIVES OF BEVERLY HILLS) joins Anna and Sim for an all-new episode of Unqualified! Plus, our GAPPS contest winner, Lindsay, is here! First, Anna and Erika reveal their thoughts on marriage and the group discusses the differences between raising a boy vs. a girl. Then, a conversation on female grooming trends before Erika answers some deal breakers and describes her experience on Real Housewives of Beverly Hills. After that, Anna hosts a new rendition of “F*ck, Marry, Kill” and listeners get a surprise appearance from Jack. Later, they call Kaitlyn, who is going through a sexual dry spell with her boyfriend. Enjoy!
